erclaw-sampler-architecture.md`, and add a one-page artistic-intent doc `docs/cypherclaw-sampler-artistic-intent.md`. (~6h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~24 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~12 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ### Sprint 3: Improvement Engine Hardening\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n **Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System), Sprint 2 (Improvement Engine Hardening)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-019** [T1] Enforce role-filter gating across R1–R8 with a single shared contract; verify machine identity preservation end-to-end. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-020** [T1] Integrate partitura for phrase-feature extraction: harmonic_charge, melodic_charge, metric_weight, cadential detection, contour apex. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-021** [T1] Implement R9 Motif Memory: LRU cache of motif hashes with variation menu and return-home decay. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-022** [T1] Implement R10 Silence Budget: per-voice and per-section accumulators enforced at phrase boundaries. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-023** [T1] Implement wind/voice lung-capacity constraints: 4–8 s continuous-play cap per instrument-sim voice. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-024** [T1] Implement R11 Call-Response Gating: follower phrase intent complements leader's realized performance. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-025** [T1] Compose SectionEnvelope with phrase arcs multiplicatively so section-level tempo elasticity modulates phrase-level shaping. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-026** [T1] Implement tempo-dependent swing curve per Friberg/Sundström (3.5:1 at slow tempi down toward 1:1 at fast), with short-note near-constant ~100 ms. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-027** [T1] Add arc-shape variety so not every phrase uses a symmetric parabola: per-phrase random selection from parabolic/cosine/asymmetric-Bezier/flat/inverted with peak-position variance. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-028** [T1] Implement restraint parameter enforced as global dampener across rules. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-014** [T2] Add systemd unit `cypherclaw-sample-capture.service` that runs `sample_capture_daemon.py` with `Restart=always`, dependent on `cypherclaw-jack.service`. (~6h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-015** [T1] Implement TDD-grade test fixtures with canned 1-second audio windows representing each detector branch (silence, footsteps, dishwasher, music, dogs, transient cluster) for fast deterministic CI. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-016** [T1] Wire `SampleSelector` into `cast_planner.select_cast_ids` so when the cast includes `sw_sampler`, a sample is pre-selected for the piece and attached to the cast metadata. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-017** [T1] Per-mode sampler density gates: composer plays `floor(sampler_density * total_phrases) + Bernoulli(sampler_density)` sampler events per piece (clamped 0..total). (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-018** [T1] When a human plays the MIDI keyboard or Theramini for >5 seconds during a song, capture that input phrase to `samples/keyboard/` or `samples/theramini/` with full tagging. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-019** [T1] Sample-aware harmonic planning: when a sample with known `pitch_hz` is selected, transpose to fit the current piece's key by computing the closest in-key root and applying `pitch_transpose_semitones`. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-020** [T1] Add per-mode effects-bus presets: solitary/evening favor more reverb + delay; working_ambience uses minimal effects; storm uses high freeze + heavy comb-B. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-021** [T2] Surface \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"currently sampling X\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"playing sample Y from source Z\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" in `operator_diagnosti