mpler\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"`, `voice.role = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sampler\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"`, default register, and per-mode gain overrides. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-032** [T1] Implement `sw_sampler.scd` granular SynthDef with bufnum, grain-size, density, position-scrub, pitch-transpose, attack/release envelope, and effects-bus send. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n *Subtotal: ~27 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n@@ -80,18 +75,16 @@ Sprints are sequential. Tasks within a sprint can run in parallel unless a depen\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n **Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-038** [T2] Couple narrative engine to SectionEnvelope selection so dramatic arcs drive section choice. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-039** [T2] Build audio-rendered SSM + Foote novelty cross-check via librosa on the actual rendered audio. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-040** [T2] Establish listener-review workflow: weekly rendered pieces tagged with rule-stack provenance, ablation tooling documented for operators, review log template in place. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-033** [T2] Migrate Anthony's existing recorded music + handpicked field recordings into `samples/library/` with appropriate metadata. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~18 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~6 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ---\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ## Requirements Coverage\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **MUST requirements:** 37/37 covered\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **SHOULD requirements:** 3 included as stretch\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **MUST requirements:** 32/32 covered\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **SHOULD requirements:** 1 included as stretch\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n **✓ All MUST requirements covered.**\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\\n./sdp/logs/Lead_T-001_20260425T183959Zd_1777146814.log:sdp/task-graph.md:46:| 16 | T-016 | Wir