tClaw Implements Each Dimension\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/startup-wizard.md:148:- Test, drill, and copied task-run subprocesses are prevented from messaging the live operator chat by default. `my-claw/tools/telegram.py` suppresses sends under `pytest`, `PROMPTCLAW_TEST_MODE`, or tmpfs task-run workdirs unless `PROMPTCLAW_ALLOW_LIVE_TELEGRAM=1` is set explicitly.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+sdp/templates/gemini/lead_t2.md:19:1.  **Explore**: Use `grep` or `rg` to find relevant files. Read up to 10 files to understand the context. Do not read more.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+sdp/templates/gemini/lead_t2.md:20:2.  **Implement**: Write the code to satisfy the request. Focus on a direct solution.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+sdp/templates/gemini/lead_t2.md:21:3.  **Test**: Add or modify tests to cover the new code.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-musicianship-roadmap.md:77:Implementation targets:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-musicianship-roadmap.md:110:Implementation targets:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-musicianship-roadmap.md:146:Implementation targets:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-musicianship-roadmap.md:179:Implementation targets:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-musicianship-roadmap.md:211:Implementation targets:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-musicianship-roadmap.md:244:Implementation targets:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-musicianship-roadmap.md:270:Implementation targets:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-musicianship-roadmap.md:296:Implementation targets:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-musicianship-roadmap.md:481:## What To Implement Next\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+sdp/logs/Lead_T-021_20260416T043834Z_1776337659.log:15:3. **`tests/test_self_critique.py`** — Added `TestPipelineIntegration` class with 3 tests:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-score-tree-composition-spec.md:192:Tests:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-score-tree-composition-spec.md:231:Tests:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-score-tree-composition-spec.md:278:Tests:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+docs/cypherclaw-score-tree-composition-spec.