+   VERIFY: `pytest tests/test_pal_cli_fake_client.py::test_pal_agent_actions_cli_executes_approved_fake_client_action -q`
+
+3. Fake-client CLI tests cover a read-only PAL workflow command through
+   `main(...)` and assert workflow metadata, executed tools, and artifacts are
+   produced without live PAL infrastructure.
+   VERIFY: `pytest tests/test_pal_cli_fake_client.py::test_pal_restart_validation_workflow_cli_uses_fake_client_and_writes_artifact -q`
+
+4. Fake-client CLI tests cover `pal deploy plan` through `main(...)` with a
+   local fake remote inventory and assert dry-run/no-write metadata.
+   VERIFY: `pytest tests/test_pal_cli_fake_client.py::test_pal_deploy_plan_cli_uses_fake_inventory_without_router_client -q`
